#include<stdio.h>

using namespace std;

int main()
{
    register int firsto=-1,secondo=-1,thirdo=-1,fortho=-1;
    char clear_buffer[100];
    while(scanf("%d.%d.%d.%d",&firsto,&secondo,&thirdo,&fortho)!=-1)
    {
        gets(clear_buffer);
        if(firsto>255 || secondo>255 || thirdo>255 || fortho > 255 || firsto<1 || secondo<0 ||thirdo <0 || fortho<0 || (firsto==255 && secondo==255 && thirdo==255 && fortho==255))
        {
            printf("Invalid\n");
        }
        else
        {
            if(firsto<128)
                printf("Class A\n");
            else if(firsto >127 && firsto <192)
                printf("Class B\n");
            else if(firsto >191 && firsto <224)
                printf("Class C\n");
            else if(firsto >223 && firsto <240)
                printf("Class D\n");
            else if(firsto >239 && firsto <256)
                printf("Class E\n");
        }

    }
    return 0;
}
